actual_result: "All services up 4+ days, queue drained to 0, 31318 events in Postgres, synthetic event verified end-to-end, 6 Prometheus targets up, pm health telemetry probe ok"
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-01T19:32:36.541Z",cursor-agent,"Stack verification complete (2026-05-01): All 9 Docker services healthy and up 4+ days. Telemetry API healthz returns ok. Grafana API health returns 200. RabbitMQ queue fully drained (0/0/1 consumer). Postgres contains 31,318 events spanning 2026-04-25 to 2026-05-01. Prometheus scraping 6 active targets (all up). Synthetic event accepted by API, processed through queue, persisted in Postgres. Local pm health --check-telemetry reports ok=true with probe=ok and queue_draining=true. Full report at scripts/prod/telemetry/reports/2026-05-01-stack-verification.md."
